        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>Our Process</h1>
            <p>A clear, transparent journey from initial consultation to planning approval</p>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="intro-section">
                <h2>How We Get Your Planning Permission Approved</h2>
                <p>Getting planning permission in London doesn't have to be complicated. Our proven 6-step process has helped over 500 homeowners secure approval with a 92% first-time success rate.</p>
                <p>We handle everything from initial site surveys to final submission, keeping you informed at every stage and responding quickly to any council queries.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Process -->
            <div class="timeline-container">
                <div class="timeline-line"></div>

                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">
                        <span class="step-number-digit">1</span>
                        <span class="step-number-label">FREE</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3 class="step-title">Free Consultation & Quote</h3>
                        <span class="step-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 30-60 minutes | Same day quote</span>
                        <p class="step-description">We start with a no-obligation consultation to understand your project goals, budget, and timeline. We'll discuss your property, what you want to achieve, and provide honest advice on feasibility.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What happens in this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Initial phone or video call to discuss your project</li>
                                <li>Review of your property location and planning constraints</li>
                                <li>Discussion of your budget and timeline expectations</li>
                                <li>Assessment of Permitted Development eligibility (if applicable)</li>
                                <li>Honest advice on likelihood of approval in your borough</li>
                                <li>Fixed-fee quote provided within 24 hours</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">
                        <span class="step-number-digit">2</span>
                        <span class="step-number-label">WEEK 1</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3 class="step-title">Site Survey & Measurements</h3>
                        <span class="step-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 1-2 hours on-site | Week 1</span>
                        <p class="step-description">Once you approve our quote, we arrange a professional site visit to take accurate measurements and photographs. This is essential for creating precise architectural drawings.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>What we do:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Complete measured survey of your property</li>
                                <li>Photographic record of existing building and surrounding area</li>
                                <li>Boundary and site constraint checks</li>
                                <li>Assessment of neighboring properties (for impact analysis)</li>
                                <li>Review of any existing drawings or documents you have</li>
                                <li>Discussion of design preferences and requirements</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">
                        <span class="step-number-digit">3</span>
                        <span class="step-number-label">WEEK 1-2</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3 class="step-title">Design & Architectural Drawings</h3>
                        <span class="step-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 7-10 working days</span>
                        <p class="step-description">Our team creates detailed architectural drawings to planning standards. We'll send you drafts for review and make any necessary revisions before finalizing the drawings.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>Drawings included:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Existing floor plans, elevations, and sections</li>
                                <li>Proposed floor plans, elevations, and sections</li>
                                <li>Site location plan (1:1250 or 1:2500 scale)</li>
                                <li>Site/block plan showing proposed works (1:200 or 1:500)</li>
                                <li>Roof plans (where applicable)</li>
                                <li>Design & Access Statement (for larger projects)</li>
                                <li>One round of revisions included</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">
                        <span class="step-number-digit">4</span>
                        <span class="step-number-label">WEEK 2-3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3 class="step-title">Pre-Application Checks & Review</h3>
                        <span class="step-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 2-3 days</span>
                        <p class="step-description">Before submission, we conduct thorough checks to ensure everything meets your local authority's requirements. This stage significantly reduces the chance of rejection.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>Quality checks include:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Review against local planning policies and guidelines</li>
                                <li>Check compliance with Conservation Area/Article 4 restrictions</li>
                                <li>Verification all drawings meet council standards</li>
                                <li>Preparation of supporting documents and statements</li>
                                <li>Final review with you before submission</li>
                                <li>Calculation and disclosure of all council fees</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 5 -->
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">
                        <span class="step-number-digit">5</span>
                        <span class="step-number-label">WEEK 3</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3 class="step-title">Planning Application Submission</h3>
                        <span class="step-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 1 day | Week 3</span>
                        <p class="step-description">We submit your complete application to the Planning Portal and your local council. You'll receive confirmation and a reference number within 48 hours.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>Submission includes:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Complete online submission via Planning Portal</li>
                                <li>All required drawings and supporting documents</li>
                                <li>Payment of council planning fees (paid by you directly or via us)</li>
                                <li>Formal validation by the local planning authority</li>
                                <li>Confirmation email with application reference number</li>
                                <li>Notification of site notice posting (if applicable)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Step 6 -->
                <div class="process-step">
                    <div class="step-number">
                        <span class="step-number-digit">6</span>
                        <span class="step-number-label">8 WEEKS</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3 class="step-title">Council Review & Approval</h3>
                        <span class="step-duration">‚è±Ô∏è 8 weeks (or 13 weeks for major applications)</span>
                        <p class="step-description">The council reviews your application. We monitor progress daily, respond to any queries, and keep you informed throughout the determination period.</p>
                        <div class="step-details">
                            <h4>During this stage:</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Regular updates on application progress (weekly minimum)</li>
                                <li>Immediate notification of any council queries or concerns</li>
                                <li>Preparation and submission of any additional information requested</li>
                                <li>Response to neighbour objections (if any)</li>
                                <li>Liaison with planning officer regarding any issues</li>
                                <li>Notification when decision is issued</li>
                                <li>Delivery of approved planning permission documents</li>
                                <li>Explanation of any planning conditions attached</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline Info -->
            <div class="timeline-info">
                <h3>Total Timeline: 11-14 Weeks from Start to Approval</h3>
                <p>From your initial consultation to receiving planning permission typically takes 11-14 weeks for standard applications. Larger or more complex projects may take 16-18 weeks. We'll give you a realistic timeline specific to your project and borough during your consultation.</p>
            </div>

